Anduran, most of your examples are right on track with how I was beating these guys.  Find out their bankroll, and select a minimum bet which is going to let me stay within their payrange, and still let me &quot;pass&quot; 7-8 times before I hit my maximum allowed bet.  Usually, in 30-45 minutes, I'd have their pockets depleted.  <br>
<br>
The thing to remember is that while normal &quot;casinos&quot; discourage playing system bets, most boneheads in the bazaar aren't even going to realize what the hell you're doing until they're broke.<br>
