<br>
Basically, What you are doing is doubling your bet every single time, to lower the chance that you lose exponentially, what happens is after a certain number of steps you assure yourself of winning, here's an example.<br>
<br>
johnny_scammer says out of character, &quot;casino open, ran 1000, roll over 600 and get double back&quot;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>bet 1pp</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
at this point, if you win, you win 1pp, grats you, if you lose, you step to the next level<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>bet 2pp</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
at this point, if you win ,your total bet has been 3pp, and you win back 4pp, meaning you win 1pp overall<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>bet 4pp</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
at this point, your total bet has been 7pp, and you win back 8pp (if you win) meaning your profit is 1pp.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>bet 8pp</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
can you see a trend yet?<br>
<br>
<br>
This does work, is it fool proof? No, but it's fucking close, there's more to it which i'll post when I get to work today.  You DO need a fortune to be able to pull it off with a huge assurance you wont lose however.  The problem doing it in everquest?  People log with your plat.<br>
